lightnin ' is a 1930 american pre-code comedy film directed by george melford and written by frances marion . the film stars george o'brien , madge bellamy , raymond walburn , raymond walburn , gertrude claire , charles " buddy " rogers , zasu pitts , ethel clayton , charles b. walthall , ethel clayton , charles b. walthall , ethel clayton , charles b. walthall , john boles , charles sellon and charles sellon . the film was released on july 26 , 1930 , by fox film corporation .